The paper discusses user authentication, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR). It also mentions the use of biometric sensors and message authentication codes, which are topics in cybernetics (cs.CY) and information theory (cs.IT), respectively. The paper also addresses usability issues, which is a topic in software engineering (cs.SE) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
